Project 3

All parts of the ray tracer are working as expected. 

Current implemented features are:
 * Adjustable Camera
 * Point lights, spheres, infinite planes, triangles, and smooth_triangles
 * Phong Shading and Cook-Torrance shading
 * Reflections and refractions
 * Shadows

Flags supported are:
   [width]    (optional) image width
   [height]   (optional) image height 

   -I [file]  Specify input file
   -O [file]  (optional) Specify output file 

   -p         (optional)Use phong shading
   -t         (optional)Use cook-torrance
   -s         (optional)Specify a sample rate

   --help     print out readme instructions

Times for bunny_small_tris.pov at 800x600 on a CSL lab machine
real  0m0.565s
user  0m0.470s
sys   0m0.075s

My creative scene is 'iceBot.tga'
